<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_115_r1l18">Peter Beheim von Geẏreck ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_115_r1l19">
<del rend="strikethrough">Marſchalk </del> des bẏſchoffs cʒu Paſſaw Marſchalk </ab>
</div>
